# The Vercel project (verity) has Root Directory services/web. Git deploys clone
# the repo and never include git-ignored files, but this also protects any *manual*
# CLI deploy run from the repo root: keep the multi-GB GPL-sourced X3P data cache
# and build artifacts out of the upload.
**/.verity
services/catalog/.verity
**/target
**/node_modules
**/.next
**/__pycache__
**/*.x3p
**/*.npz
